reviews.review_text:
6691 sounds better to me This is a nice recording with good highs and presence, but not as "up front" as gd80-05-06.senn.kaplan.6691.sbeok.shnf.  4 stars for me on this one.  Definitely a solid listenable contribution.

Fun show too, I love these May 80s shows!
